{"tid":2212974,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"海南禁穆斯林女學生戴頭巾","createTime":"2020-09-22T08:00:43.000Z","updateTime":"2020-09-22T08:44:33.000Z","uid":25558,"like":6,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":11,"replies":[{"pid":"ae74c33b646048805f4eb2208fb44b1a4305eeb0","tid":2212974,"uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-22T08:00:43.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/china/20200918/BOVVRRFSDRCAVNLEGJWXUXT4PQ/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fchina%2F20200918%2FBOVVRRFSDRCAVNLEGJWXUXT4PQ%2F&d=UI3sabJMorhQDzR%2BXF3zEUzKa5je2Ql9GrxhcbxOrro%3D&h=8ca12823\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fchina%2F20200918%2FBOVVRRFSDRCAVNLEGJWXUXT4PQ%2F&h=a6aec89f\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.appledaily.com/china/20200918/BOVVRRFSDRCAVNLEGJWXUXT4PQ/</a><br />\n<br />\n節錄<br />\n<br />\n海南禁穆斯林女學生戴頭巾<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/resizer/m7gmRHG14-FJj0w8XYns3cXkSvQ=/720x728/filters:quality(100)/cloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com/appledaily/7P2G3EUK4RAILAYNX6Q4M5GR34.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fresizer%2Fm7gmRHG14-FJj0w8XYns3cXkSvQ%3D%2F720x728%2Ffilters%3Aquality%28100%29%2Fcloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com%2Fappledaily%2F7P2G3EUK4RAILAYNX6Q4M5GR34.jpg&h=dc3eb0ed&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n內蒙古因中共強推漢化政策，年少學子被迫反抗捍衞母語；抗爭未了，極權魔爪再伸向海南三亞，有回族穆斯林女孩被禁止戴頭巾進入校園，公安守在校門，女生不得其門而入，只能在門外席地看書（圖），當地開始有學生罷課聲援。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n觸發學生罷課聲援<br />\n<br />\n中共只准學生頸纏紅領巾，不准穆斯林女孩戴頭巾。周二網上流出影片，其中一則地點為海南省三亞巿回輝小學，片中可見校門有多名公安把守，眾多戴頭巾的小學女生坐在門外看書，旁邊有大批家長陪同。至於另一段網上影片，則有數十名戴頭巾女學生排隊站在學校門外。。。。。。。<br />\n<br />\n網傳片段中的學校均位於三亞巿天涯區鳳凰鎮，其中回新村及回輝村住有約一萬名被當局稱為「三亞回族」的少數民族，由明末清。。。。。。。<br />\n<br />\n自由亞洲電台/寒冬"},{"pid":"d913dc27a48b2186bed341f30c3c73f05a3a2627","tid":2212974,"uid":62532,"like":1,"dislike":2,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-09-22T08:04:02.000Z","msg":"睇定d先"},